attachments.fallback: #8691 Add a better search UI for patients index page
attachments.text:
In the current patient page, we have 4 independet search on patient, at any point in time you can only search by one practically.  
Here is an how the current UI looks.  
<https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/14979190/372989032-0971d608-73f8-491a-b8e9-859c14075cd6.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..xWrzDIwYSBQN4JS6AImefjoIzTucYjFrziQnUyZF1hI|image>

Let upgrade it with a smart search compoent where the user can select what to search for.  
<https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/14979190/372989079-91099d34-5c4c-44fd-8da0-094265bbbacd.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..328wa5eXLvC0yEvdeJjiMLu1F2mooPDYt9tzm_6KWgw|image>

It should also support keyboard short cuts.  
<https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/14979190/372989101-8830e0fd-8322-4544-9e64-dd86863b2f2b.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..UX1Fh94jdeunsLzSrsCLknAl7g-U4H26puuThcTJD_I|image>

The valid options would be Name | Phone Number | OP/IP number | Emergency Contact Number.

Also reduce the height of the count box to match the component.
attachments.title: #8691 Add a better search UI for patients index page

attachments.text:
*Describe the bug*  
When CNS is opened in large 4K displays, 75% of the screen space is wasted.

*To Reproduce*  
Steps to reproduce the behavior:

1. Visit <https://care.ohc.network/facility/0c95c7f0-e1d2-4aff-83fa-933cef60d3a8/cns|https://care.ohc.network/facility/0c95c7f0-e1d2-4aff-83fa-933cef60d3a8/cns> on a 4K display

*Expected behavior*  
On large displays, render more vitals monitors into view per page.

*Screenshots*

<https://private-user-images.githubusercontent.com/25143503/278376732-98f9e3f9-7e20-42ce-a095-5abe841e88c6.png?jwt=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..vG25IhtYbmICDBMuFx1FyGUuQO7IalzC1RBoF4pWTtQ|image>

*Proposed Changes*

• Fixes <https://github.com/ohcnetwork/care_fe/issues/8691|#issue_number>

@ohcnetwork/care-fe-code-reviewers

*Merge Checklist*

• Add specs that demonstrate bug / test a new feature.
• Update <https://docs.ohc.network|product documentation>.
• Ensure that UI text is kept in I18n files.
• Prep screenshot or demo video for changelog entry, and attach it to issue.
• Request for Peer Reviews
• Completion of QA

*Summary by CodeRabbit*

*Release Notes*

• *New Features*  
   • Introduced a `SearchByMultipleFields` component for enhanced search functionality across various fields.  
   • Added new UI components for dialogs, commands, and popovers, improving user interaction and accessibility.  
   • Updated localization files to improve terminology and add new search options in English and Marathi.
• *Bug Fixes*  
   • Improved the interaction flow for patient name input in the patient management interface.
• *Chores*  
   • Updated dependencies to enhance UI component functionality.
• *Documentation*  
   • Enhanced translations for user interface elements in Marathi.
